Autograph
---------

Autograph is a CSS generation langauge that uses s-expressions for
declaring styling rules.

Example:
(defvar width 2em)

(css
 (*
  (:font-family monospace)
  (:font-weight bold)
  (:padding 0px)
  (:margin 0px)
  (:cursor pointer))
 
 ("input[type=text]"
  (:border 0px solid)
  (:font-size inherit)
  (:padding 0px)
  (:margin 0px))

 (.*Two-character-hex-value-edit-view
  `(:max-width ,width)
  (:display inline-block))
  
 (.*Edit-view
  (:width 2em)
  (:border solid 1px red))
 )
 
